            "tag": "BEST TIME",
            "heading": "Best Time to Visit",
            "description": "May to June and September to October are especially rewarding for clear views, grasslands, flowers, and plateau scenery, while winter offers quiet snowscapes and strong sunrise conditions for Meili."
          }
